name: Cube Dash (muhammadalbar)
description: Cube dash is a series of platforming video games developed for game development course. Basically, this game consists of a cube that is stuck in space and wants to go back home. In order for the cube to reach its house, the cube needs to find a suitable portal so that it can reach its house. But to reach the portal, the cube must pass through the obstacles and kill the enemies that get in the way.
